        <item>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Secondary Payer Advancement, Rationalization, and Clarification Act or the SPARC Act</strong></p> <p>This bill specifies&nbsp;recovery rules and timelines with respect to secondary claims responsibility under the Medicare prescription drug benefit. Current law specifies only that&nbsp;secondary payor provisions apply under the benefit in the same manner as they apply with respect to Medicare Advantage plans.</p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-11-20T15:13:09Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
